title: Ognjen Mitrović
text:
Ognjen Mitrović (born 30 June 1999) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FK%20Proleter%20Novi%20Sad">Proleter Novi Sad</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Serbian%20SuperLiga">Serbian SuperLiga</a> debut for <a href="FK%20Proleter%20Novi%20Sad">Proleter Novi Sad</a> on 22 July 2018 in a game against <a href="FK%20Radni%C4%8Dki%20Ni%C5%A1">Radnički Niš</a>.
